00:08:37.956 --> 00:08:39.097
⟨zey⟩ nemen

00:08:38.073 --> 00:08:39.400
ven iz dos geven?

00:08:39.350 --> 00:08:40.914
dos iz geven oykhet in

00:08:40.914 --> 00:08:43.800
in fir, onheyb fir un fertsikstn yor, dakht zikh, ye.

00:08:43.693 --> 00:08:46.505
in vinter, in kaltn vinter tsayt?

00:08:43.800 --> 00:08:45.105
an aktsye

00:08:45.651 --> 00:08:48.429
ye, un m'hot genumen oyf ESTONIA mentshn.

00:08:48.148 --> 00:08:50.352
un ve- vemen hot men genumen?

00:08:48.672 --> 00:08:53.571
m'hot tsugenumen a, efsher a tsen toyznt man, a fule. m'hot tsugenumen a sakh.

00:08:53.312 --> 00:08:54.554
in

00:08:53.571 --> 00:08:55.730
tsu mir, tsu mir iz men oykh gekumen oyf nemen

00:08:55.730 --> 00:08:58.082
hob ikh gevizn ikh hob dem SIGN, hobn zey mir nit genumen.

00:08:57.852 --> 00:09:00.107
un ayer, ayer shvester bruder?

00:08:58.082 --> 00:08:59.902
der SIGN hot mir geratevet.

00:08:59.902 --> 00:09:01.822
NO, NO, dan hot men kinder nit genumen.

00:09:01.822 --> 00:09:03.257
 di kinder zaynen geblibn.

00:09:03.257 --> 00:09:05.552
nor oyf ESTONIA hot men avekgefirt mentshn.

00:09:05.395 --> 00:09:08.156
un, un m'hot zey gefirt tsum toyt?

00:09:05.552 --> 00:09:07.059
zaynen tsurik nit gekumen.

00:09:07.234 --> 00:09:11.095
me arbet un s'iz keyner nit gekumen tsurik. zeyer a shreklekher lager geven.

00:09:11.095 --> 00:09:12.437
zeyer shreklekh.

00:09:12.437 --> 00:09:15.731
ikh hob gehat dem SIGN, UNK arayngegangen. ikh hob gevizn dem SIGN

00:09:15.731 --> 00:09:16.781
hot men nit genumen.

00:09:16.549 --> 00:09:18.737
ober s'iz nisht geven keyn ah

00:09:18.827 --> 00:09:20.053
keyn shkhite?

00:09:19.873 --> 00:09:23.659
ne- nit dortn oyf an ort. hot avekgefirt oyf ESTONIA mentshn far mayn tsayt.

00:09:23.659 --> 00:09:25.658
shvester mit di briderl nokh geven

00:09:25.658 --> 00:09:27.907
UNK di kinder hot men gehaltn in a kind-

00:09:27.907 --> 00:09:30.747
m'hot gemakht sotsyale hilf iz geven. m'hot geholfn

00:09:30.747 --> 00:09:34.210
di kinder zoln UNK nit zayn oyfn gas, me zol nit zen az s'iz do kinder.

00:09:33.272 --> 00:09:37.771
iz aykh geven a khidesh vos far a, vos far a gezelshaft iz geven?

00:09:35.044 --> 00:09:37.749
un di kinder zaynen geven zeyer klug.

00:09:37.749 --> 00:09:39.664
v- ver hot gezogt gezelshaft?

00:09:39.567 --> 00:09:44.758
⟨az alts⟩ iz geven ki- iz geven teater, kino, un azoy vayter?

00:09:39.664 --> 00:09:41.822
UNK rateven zikh nor.

00:09:42.385 --> 00:09:46.015
ah, dos iz geven, zey hobn gehat dos, in, in geto. d- di men-

00:09:45.287 --> 00:09:46.040
yo

00:09:46.015 --> 00:09:46.995
zey hobn gehat

00:09:46.995 --> 00:09:49.575
zey hobn gehat farsheydene unternemungen eyder mir zaynen gekumen

00:09:49.575 --> 00:09:52.375
ober mir zaynen nit geven ⟨genumen⟩ onteyl in di zakhn. s'iz geven

00:09:52.375 --> 00:09:54.205
m'hot zey gemakht freylekh aleyn

00:09:54.205 --> 00:09:55.705
shoyn geven di zakhn.

00:09:54.636 --> 00:09:58.834
m'hot gelernt di kind- ayer, a- zogt az er bruder iz gegangen in a

00:09:55.705 --> 00:09:56.472
UNK

00:09:56.472 --> 00:09:59.071
mayn bruder hot gelernt, a fakh shule.

00:09:58.834 --> 00:10:00.181
a fakh shule.

00:09:59.071 --> 00:10:01.734
m'hot gelernt di kinder dortn, a blekher

00:10:02.027 --> 00:10:06.546
blekheray. er, er hot gornisht nit gekent, er hot nit ge- az er hot nit gelernt in gantsn

00:10:06.546 --> 00:10:08.470
nor dortn gelernt blekheray

00:10:08.470 --> 00:10:12.689
un di shvester gelernt shnayderay in kinderheym. mayn shvester bashraybt dos.

00:10:12.689 --> 00:10:14.779
fun di kinderheym. ikh bin nit geven dort.

00:10:14.869 --> 00:10:17.259
iz zaynen geven in kinderheym di kinder

00:10:17.417 --> 00:10:20.870
nu, un dernokh iz geven di aktsye fun di kleyne kinder.

00:10:21.670 --> 00:10:23.260
ikh hob gearbet in vesheray.

00:10:23.260 --> 00:10:26.440
a vokh hob ikh gearbet in der fri, un a vokh hob ikh gearbet bay nakht

00:10:26.935 --> 00:10:27.975
in vesheray.

00:10:28.369 --> 00:10:31.991
in, un, un azoy iz ongegangen, ye?

00:10:31.845 --> 00:10:33.779
vos iz geven di aktsye?

00:10:33.060 --> 00:10:35.433
di aktsye iz ongekumen in MARCH.

00:10:35.676 --> 00:10:37.594
in MARCH, iz dos iz di yortsayt.

00:10:36.283 --> 00:10:37.542
fir un fertsik.

00:10:38.123 --> 00:10:41.627
iz geven di aktsye fun kleyne kinder. dos hot pasirt.

00:10:39.287 --> 00:10:40.749
un vos hot pasirt?

00:10:41.920 --> 00:10:42.981
vos iz geven?

00:10:42.981 --> 00:10:46.921
s'iz in der fri, mir hobn oyfgeshtanen, iz geven UNK der hilkher, ir veyst dokh

00:10:46.921 --> 00:10:48.411
vos me redt, durkh a

00:10:48.467 --> 00:10:50.809
hot men geshrien "ale zoln arayn in di hayzer."

00:10:50.809 --> 00:10:52.798
zol keyner nit zayn oyfn gas.

00:10:53.108 --> 00:10:58.057
un mir hobn gevoynt punkt baym, baym toyer nit vayt, UNK ikh hob gehat mayn v- di voynung.

00:10:58.057 --> 00:10:59.396
nit vayt fun toyer.

00:10:59.402 --> 00:11:03.311
ale zoln arayngeyn in di hayzer, un ale zoln dort bahal- ale zoln zayn in shtub.

00:11:03.351 --> 00:11:05.336
dernokh iz arayn a gantse armey

00:11:05.713 --> 00:11:09.034
un me, m'hot gegebn a ORDER, der aher un der ahin

00:11:07.890 --> 00:11:09.065
daytshe?

00:11:09.034 --> 00:11:12.044
dos iz geven v- vaysrusn dakht zikh, ongeton

00:11:12.044 --> 00:11:14.924
in grine zakhn, azoy vi di vaysrusn, UNK soldatn

00:11:14.924 --> 00:11:16.442
a gantse armey arayn

00:11:16.442 --> 00:11:19.117
un s'iz arayngeforn groyse mashines

00:11:19.117 --> 00:11:21.249
ot do azoy vi di UNK mashines

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:27.369
tsu, m'hot gegebn a ORDER di zoln geyn in dem zayt un di in dem zayt un di in dem zayt.

00:11:27.369 --> 00:11:29.585
ale, mir, mir veysn vos do kumt for.

00:11:29.845 --> 00:11:33.115
mir zaynen arayn ale in di hayzer. mir hobn gezen durkhn fentster

00:11:33.115 --> 00:11:34.749
az me firt kinder

00:11:35.228 --> 00:11:38.059
un mames, alte mentshn

00:11:38.059 --> 00:11:39.288
un kinder firt men.

00:11:39.835 --> 00:11:42.379
m'iz arayn tsu undz in shtub. mir hobn gevoynt punkt baym

00:11:42.379 --> 00:11:43.308
baym toyer

00:11:43.308 --> 00:11:45.094
in a bara- in aza groysn

00:11:45.285 --> 00:11:46.528
dos iz shoyn geve-

00:11:46.703 --> 00:11:49.852
geven nit in di MOVIE, bay mir iz shoyn ibergegangen di MOVIE

00:11:49.943 --> 00:11:51.658
nit in ⟨dort⟩ vu ikh hob geven frier.

00:11:51.850 --> 00:11:53.610
vayl di geto iz dokh gevorn klener.

00:11:53.318 --> 00:11:57.058
un vu za- vu zayt ir geven demolt, in a dire?

00:11:53.610 --> 00:11:55.286
m'hot dokh avekgefirt mentshn.

00:11:56.187 --> 00:11:58.040
in a dire. mir hobn gehat epes a

00:11:58.040 --> 00:11:59.854
in, in aza dire, in a voynung

00:11:59.854 --> 00:12:02.866
un s'iz geven m- di dire hot zikh gefunen nit vayt fun UNK

00:12:02.866 --> 00:12:05.608
iz dos oykh der yudnrat hot gegebn a voynung vu tsu voynen

00:12:05.608 --> 00:12:06.544
aynteyl

00:12:06.544 --> 00:12:10.130
bin ikh geven mit mit mayn sh- shvester bruder geven in

00:12:10.130 --> 00:12:12.380
in sh- in dortn vu ikh zog aykh.

00:12:12.353 --> 00:12:14.068
UNK in velkher gas gedenkt ir?

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:16.971
ikh veys nit. UNK mayn shvester bashraybt dos. zi iz geven in kinderheym.

00:12:17.027 --> 00:12:19.697
nor ikh bin geven un s'iz geven nokh a, mit mir

00:12:19.697 --> 00:12:22.867
eyne a Svirer meydl mit a mamen an alte

00:12:22.867 --> 00:12:26.356
un s'iz geven a, a, a Kovner froy mit eyn yingl

00:12:26.356 --> 00:12:28.227
vos alemen hot men shoyn oysgeharget.

00:12:28.227 --> 00:12:30.007
zi iz shoyn geblibn nor mit eyn zun.

00:12:30.007 --> 00:12:31.550
a tsvelf yorikn BOY.

00:12:31.962 --> 00:12:33.806
un s'iz geven nokh eyne a froy

00:12:33.806 --> 00:12:36.742
vos zi hot gehat a kleynem yingele efsher fun akht yor

00:12:36.742 --> 00:12:38.823
a SMARTe BOYtshikl

00:12:39.606 --> 00:12:43.214
oy, d- vos iz geven mi- mit di froy, a kluginker ⟨iz er⟩.

00:12:40.315 --> 00:12:41.811
a kluger yingl?

00:12:43.214 --> 00:12:45.494
vos iz geven mit dem yingele, mit ir?

00:12:45.494 --> 00:12:47.998
di froy hot oysgezen vi a goye, vi a litvi- a-

00:12:47.998 --> 00:12:51.516
iz a, epes a por vokhn far dem, a khoydesh

00:12:51.516 --> 00:12:52.613
iz zi aroys

00:12:52.613 --> 00:12:54.315
oyfn arishe zayt

00:12:54.355 --> 00:12:56.559
un zi iz ⟨aroys litviner⟩ bahaltn zikh

00:12:56.970 --> 00:12:58.111
mitn yingele.

00:12:58.118 --> 00:12:59.040
gut.

00:12:59.434 --> 00:13:02.696
dernokh hot zikh meyashev geven, darf kumen in geto, zi vil nokh

00:13:02.696 --> 00:13:06.839
zi iz UNK vayl zi UNK epes fardinen a por oyfn mark, veys

00:13:06.839 --> 00:13:09.081
s'iz ve- dem yingele hot zi gelozn bay di goyim

00:13:09.087 --> 00:13:11.072
aleyn iz zi gekumen tsurik in geto.

00:13:11.432 --> 00:13:14.193
zi hot oysgezen vi a goyke, di, nit keyn ⟨inyen⟩

00:13:14.588 --> 00:13:17.958
un, un do iz men gekumen di daytshn, un ir yingele

00:13:17.958 --> 00:13:21.998
vos hot er geton? er iz dortn geven bay a goy, un er hot ⟨zikh⟩ aroysgeganvet fun shtub

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:23.882
er hot oyfgehoybn di drotn

00:13:23.882 --> 00:13:26.108
un er hot gezogt er vil mer nit zayn, er vil kumen in geto.

00:13:26.108 --> 00:13:27.668
er geyt ⟨nit⟩ tsurik in geto.

00:13:27.668 --> 00:13:29.567
un der yingele iz gekumen tsurik tsu ir.

00:13:29.978 --> 00:13:32.000
zi hot gekhalesht, geven meshuge

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:35.304
az, az UNK yingele gekumen. zi hot dokh im ibergelozn dortn.

00:13:35.310 --> 00:13:37.514
nor er hot nit gevelt zayn baym goy, bay di goyim.

00:13:38.213 --> 00:13:42.054
i- ⟨hot⟩ men gekumen tsu undz in shtub, hot men tsugenumen dem yingele bay ir

00:13:42.685 --> 00:13:46.841
un m'hot tsugenumen bay di froy dem yingl. eyn yingl geblibn bay ir, alemen oysgeharget.

00:13:46.841 --> 00:13:49.395
a eltere froy, Khaye ⟨Osipovitsh⟩ hot zi geheysn.

00:13:49.620 --> 00:13:51.540
tsugenumen eyn yingl bay ir

00:13:51.540 --> 00:13:54.070
di, di Svirer iz geven mit a mamen

00:13:54.177 --> 00:13:55.532
un ikh bin geven

00:13:55.532 --> 00:13:58.662
mit mayne beyde kinder, zaynen gekumen tsu mir ⟨ven⟩ s'iz gevorn der tuml

00:13:58.662 --> 00:14:00.330
hot men tselozn ale kinder.

00:14:00.589 --> 00:14:04.923
m'hot z- m'hot UNK gehat moyre tsu haltn zey in fakh shule, farshteyt?

00:14:04.923 --> 00:14:07.789
hobn di kinder gekumen tsurik tsu mir. me hot ale kinder tselozn.

00:14:07.862 --> 00:14:10.483
vayle m'hot, m'hot nit gevust UNK oyf di kinder

00:14:10.483 --> 00:14:12.280
zaynen tsu mir gekumen beyde kinder.

00:14:12.280 --> 00:14:14.404
der daytsh iz arayn tsu undz in shtub

00:14:14.427 --> 00:14:16.969
un er hot gezogt azoy, "RAUS, alemen."

00:14:17.515 --> 00:14:18.808
hot genumen tseyln.

00:14:19.050 --> 00:14:21.190
mayne beyde kinder zoln geyn.

00:14:21.190 --> 00:14:23.365
di froy mit dem yingl, zi zol geyn.

00:14:23.365 --> 00:14:25.465
der kleyner yingele vos iz gekumen tsurik

00:14:25.465 --> 00:14:27.467
un mi- un mir hot er gezogt

00:14:27.467 --> 00:14:29.206
 "⟨mir hot er tsayt⟩.

00:14:29.206 --> 00:14:30.874
mir ⟨dernemt, dernemt⟩ nokh nit."

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:33.449
un, un di froy's, di mamen

00:14:33.449 --> 00:14:36.804
hot zi nit gez- nit gevelt gebn di mamen UNK, mayn mame UNK

00:14:36.804 --> 00:14:38.984
vu, vu vestu nemen mame? ikh gib nit.

00:14:38.984 --> 00:14:40.580
hot er tsebrokhn oyf ir

00:14:40.580 --> 00:14:45.133
a gumene nagayke, e- er hot ir azoy geshlogn un aroysgerisn di mamen fun ir

00:14:45.223 --> 00:14:47.529
un avekgefirt in di mashines.

00:14:48.109 --> 00:14:53.081
ikh bin gelofn tsum mashin, zogt er az mir nemt er nit. mir veln nokh USEn dir oyf arbet.

00:14:53.155 --> 00:14:54.971
mir kenen dir USEn oyf arbet.

00:14:55.062 --> 00:14:56.473
mir hobn tsayt mit dir.

00:14:56.766 --> 00:14:59.578
un al- un di kinder zaynen arayngegangen ale in di mashines.

00:14:59.685 --> 00:15:00.981
s'iz aroysgegangen

00:15:00.023 --> 00:15:02.261
ayer shvester un ayer bruder?

00:15:00.981 --> 00:15:03.462
tsvey, briderl, tsvey toyznt man

00:15:03.462 --> 00:15:05.045
kinder hot men tsugenumen dem tog.

00:15:05.338 --> 00:15:07.369
ale kinderlekh nebekh tsugenu-

00:15:07.369 --> 00:15:09.737
s'iz geven a froy, m- mayn shtetl iz zi UNK

00:15:09.777 --> 00:15:13.348
ikh hob ir getrofn nokh di milkhome, a mesh- zi iz in gantsn meshuge geven.

00:15:13.573 --> 00:15:16.520
a onshtendike froy, der man iz geven in yudnrat

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:19.312
un zi, un zi hot gearbet in vesheray oykhet no-

00:15:19.312 --> 00:15:21.442
zi hot gearbet m- bay tog

00:15:21.589 --> 00:15:25.242
un bay nakht, ikh hob gearbet bay nakht, un bay tog nit geven.

00:15:25.242 --> 00:15:26.812
a vokh azoy, a vokh azoy.

00:15:26.812 --> 00:15:30.273
un gehat dray pupes sheyne kinder, a yingele mit tsvey meydelekh.

00:15:30.988 --> 00:15:32.956
oy, iz gekumen tsu geyn

00:15:31.545 --> 00:15:33.575
vos hot ir gemeynt vet zayn

00:15:33.575 --> 00:15:35.353
vo- vos vet forkumen?

00:15:35.224 --> 00:15:37.937
vos me- mir hobn gevu- az zay nemen tsu di kinder.

00:15:37.937 --> 00:15:41.776
zey nemen tsu di kinder oyf, m'hot gevust az zey nemen tsu oyf hargenen di kinder alemen.

00:15:41.417 --> 00:15:43.976
dos hot alemen gevust? ir hot gevust?

00:15:41.776 --> 00:15:46.410
kinder un alte. avade. vos vet men ton mit di kinder, mit di, mit di eltere?

00:15:46.410 --> 00:15:46.990
s'iz

00:15:46.990 --> 00:15:52.390
di litviner zaynen geshtanen arum di drotn un ⟨mit, mit⟩ zeyere kinder UNK gevizn az zey hobn di kinder

00:15:52.390 --> 00:15:54.557
un dortn avekgefirt mashines mit kinder

00:15:54.394 --> 00:15:55.471
un ah

00:15:55.471 --> 00:15:57.222
un di soldatn hobn

00:15:57.010 --> 00:16:03.335
di soldatn hobn geholfn UNK, geholfn, tsegangen zikh iber ale, ale ekn. s'iz geven a groyser geto.

00:16:03.335 --> 00:16:05.207
zey hobn UNK nit gezen keyn soldatn

00:16:05.207 --> 00:16:08.697
nor m'hot geholfn arayn- araynfirn di kinder. andere hobn getrogn oyf di hent.

00:16:07.995 --> 00:16:09.553
zey hobn nisht geleyknt?

00:16:09.553 --> 00:16:13.068
zay hobn op- nisht opgeleyknt az zey nemen di kinder tsum hargenen?

00:16:09.730 --> 00:16:10.250
vo-

00:16:12.754 --> 00:16:14.283
zey hobn nit gezogt oyf hargenen.

00:16:14.408 --> 00:16:15.442
dos nit.

00:16:15.442 --> 00:16:16.851
hargenen hot men nit gezogt, nor

00:16:16.851 --> 00:16:19.227
zey nemen tsu ale kinder un alte layt.

00:16:19.268 --> 00:16:21.742
di gzeyre UNK alte mentshn

00:16:20.533 --> 00:16:22.839
zey hobn gegebn a terets far dem?

00:16:22.322 --> 00:16:23.990
di, keyn terets nit.

00:16:23.990 --> 00:16:27.565
ho- do- d- di froy fun mayn shtetl UNK ir man geven in yudnrat

00:16:27.621 --> 00:16:31.963
iz gehat dray pupes, tsvey n- gerotene kinder, tsvey meydelekh mit a yingele

00:16:31.963 --> 00:16:34.820
hob ikh aleyn gezen vi dem yingele hobn zey getrogn oyfn hant.

00:16:35.181 --> 00:16:38.232
der daytsh hot getrogn, a keyner yingele hot nit gekent WALKen tsum

00:16:38.232 --> 00:16:40.991
hot men ar- getrogn, arayngeleygt in mashin arayngefirt

00:16:40.991 --> 00:16:42.819
un mayn shvesterl iz oykh geven in mashin.

00:16:43.213 --> 00:16:46.078
un, un, un s'iz avekgeforn, ale, ale

00:16:45.103 --> 00:16:46.346
un ayer bruder.

00:16:46.078 --> 00:16:47.189
⟨iz⟩ avekgeforn.

00:16:46.757 --> 00:16:47.560
UNK

00:16:47.314 --> 00:16:49.653
bay nakht iz gekumen tsu mir a yid

00:16:49.693 --> 00:16:52.246
un er zogt "do voynt Abramovitsh?" zog ikh ye.

00:16:52.246 --> 00:16:53.704
ayer a shvester iz do.

00:16:53.811 --> 00:16:55.205
shtel zikh for

00:16:55.397 --> 00:16:57.854
az mayn shvester iz aroys fun di mashines

00:16:57.878 --> 00:16:58.913
⟨kent⟩ ir gleybn?

00:16:58.913 --> 00:17:00.639
eyne fun toyznter kinder.

00:17:00.831 --> 00:17:03.272
der briderl hot nit gekent geyn. er iz tsu kleyn geven

00:17:03.295 --> 00:17:06.461
un zi zogt, zi iz geven in mashin, zi bashraybt dort in bikhl

00:17:06.501 --> 00:17:08.756
un di mashin hot geshpilt muzik

00:17:09.268 --> 00:17:11.827
un di kinder hobn geveynt. muzik iz geven.

00:17:11.884 --> 00:17:13.126
far vos muzik?

00:17:11.917 --> 00:17:13.885
kind- m- muzik.

